Title: [Critical] Ransomware Detected on Server-X

Description:
A ransomware-related file (crypto_locker.exe) was detected on a production server. The file exhibited malicious behavior including encryption activity. 
The system showed abnormal process execution and potential data compromise.

Indicators of Compromise (IOCs):
File Name: crypto_locker.exe
Source IP: 192.168.1.50
Hash: 44d88612fea8a8f36de82e1278abb02f

Priority: Critical

Status: Open

Assigned To: SOC Analyst

Steps Taken:
- Isolated affected system from network
- Identified malicious file and process
- Collected basic system information

Next Actions:
- Perform full malware analysis
- Restore affected systems from backup
- Monitor network for lateral movement

Escalation Email:

Dear Tier 2 Team,

